unk_28bc3c5.value:
function Start(idActorPlayer, sLevelAreaName)
	if(Hydra.ActorIsAlive(idActorPlayer)) then
		--Boss Respawn Trigger Enabled
		Hydra.ActorEnable(BOSS_TRIGGER)
	end
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	if(Hydra.ActorIsAlive(idActor)) then
		--Disable Trigger
		Hydra.ActorDisable(BOSS_TRIGGER)
		--Send Event
		Hydra.EventSend("QST_Step_AbarhuRift_GenbarEnc_Start")
	end
end

function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)
	--Reset Boss Encounter
	local boss = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "BOSS")
	for i, bossID in ipairs(boss) do
		Hydra.ActorEnable(bossID)
		Hydra.ActorSetNeverDie(bossID, true)
		Hydra.ActorClearAnimSetOverride(bossID)
	end	
	--Enable Demon Spawners
	local demon = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "SPAWNERS")
	for i, demonID in ipairs(demon) do
		Hydra.ActorEnable(demonID)
	end	
	--Manually Start Encounter
	Hydra.BossEncounterManuallyQueueStart(BOSS_LEVEL_AREA)
end

function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)

	--Stop Spawners/Kill Demon Adds
	local demon = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("Step_Saga_CultistCanyon_Adds")
	for i, demonID in ipairs(demon) do
		Hydra.ActorDelete(demonID)
	end
	
end

function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)

--Empower Genbar on Megademon death, if alive
	local boss = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "BOSS")
	if Hydra.ActorIsAlive(boss) then
		Hydra.BuffApplyToTarget("MonsterAffix_Teleporter", "MonsterAffix_Teleporter", boss)
	end
	
end

unk_98d4504.value:
--Conclude Boss Encounter, removing fog walls/portal restrictions
Hydra.BossEncounterManuallyComplete(BOSS_LEVEL_AREA)

Hydra.QuestAdvancePhase()

unk_28bc3c5.value:
function Start(sWorldName, sLevelAreaName)
	--Reset Boss Encounter
	--Enable Genbar and Demon
	Hydra.ActorFadeAndDelete(ID_GENBAR, 2)
	Hydra.ActorFadeAndDelete(ID_MEGADEMON, 2)
	--Enable Demon Spawners
	local demon = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "SPAWNERS")
	for i, demonID in ipairs(demon) do
		Hydra.ActorFadeAndDelete(demonID, 2);
	end
end

function Start(idActor, flPrevHP, flHp)

	--Make Genbar immortal/untargetable and move to summoning area
	local boss = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "BOSS")
	
	for i, bossID in ipairs(boss) do
		Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtFeet(bossID, POWER_KNOCKBACK)
		Hydra.ActorSetNoDamage(bossID, true)
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(bossID, false)
		Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(bossID, false)
		Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(bossID)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(bossID, GENBAR_SUMMON_MARKER, "NPC_Run", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(bossID, GENBAR_SUMMON_MARKER)
	
		Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(bossID)
		Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(bossID, S_GENBAR_CRYOUT_ANIMSET)
		Hydra.QActorPlaySimpleConversation(CONV_GENBAR_SUMMON, bossID)
		Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(bossID)
	end
	
	
	
	--Genbar consumes any remaining demons
	local spawners = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "SPAWNERS")
	for i, spawnerID in ipairs(spawners) do
		Hydra.ActorDisable(spawnerID)
	end	
	
	local demon = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("Step_Saga_CultistCanyon_Adds")
	for i, demonID in ipairs(demon) do
		Hydra.ActorKill(demonID)
	end

end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	--Disembodied Elias
	local tParticipants = Hydra.QuestGetParticipants()
	for i, idParticipant in ipairs(tParticipants) do
		Hydra.ActorPlayDisembodiedConversation(CONV_ELIAS_CALLOUT, idParticipant)
	end
	Hydra.WaitForConversationFinished(CONV_ELIAS_CALLOUT)

	--Enable Megademon and make Genbar active again
	Hydra.EventSendToActor("QST_Step_AbarhuRift_GenbarEnc_DemonSummon", idSelf, idSelf)
	Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(ID_MEGADEMON, false)
	
end

function Start(idActorSpawned, idActorSpawner)
	--Slight pause for pacing
	Hydra.ActorSetNoDamage(idActorSpawned, true)
	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idActorSpawned, false)
	Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(idActorSpawned, false)
	Hydra.ActorSetNeverDie(idActorSpawned, true)
	
	Hydra.Wait(1)
	Hydra.EventSend("QST_Step_CCanyon_GenbarEnc_LorathBark")
	-- Enable the Megademon
	Hydra.ActorSetNoDamage(idActorSpawned, false)
	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idActorSpawned, true)
	Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(idActorSpawned, true)
	Hydra.ActorSetNeverDie(idActorSpawned, false)
	
	--Enable Genbar to restart fight
	local boss = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "BOSS")
	
	for i, bossID in ipairs(boss) do
		Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(bossID)
		Hydra.ActorSetNoDamage(bossID, false)
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(bossID, true)
		Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(bossID, true)
		Hydra.ActorSetNeverDie(bossID, false)
	end
end

function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)

--Empower Megademon on Genbar death, if alive
	if Hydra.ActorIsAlive(ID_MEGADEMON) then
		Hydra.BuffApplyToTarget("MonsterAffix_ShadowEnchanted", "MonsterAffix_ShadowEnchanted", ID_MEGADEMON)
	end
	
end

function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)

--Summon Megademon Effect
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(DEMON_SUMMON_MARKER, S_EFFECTGROUP_DEMON_SUMMON, true)
	Hydra.Wait(2.0)
	Hydra.ActorRemoveComplexEffectByEffectGroupSNO(DEMON_SUMMON_MARKER, S_EFFECTGROUP_DEMON_SUMMON)
	
end

function Start(idActorSummoner, idActorSummoned, sPowerName)

--Add Summon to Summon Group
	Hydra.ActorAddToGroup(idActorSummoned, "Step_Saga_CultistCanyon_Adds")
	Hydra.BuffApplyToTarget(Hydra.ReferencePower("generic_deathAppend_unsummonEffect"), "BUFF_UNSUMMON_DEATH_DEMONIC", idActorSummoned)
end
